snippet.title: The Callisto Protocol Gameplay Reveal Trailer | gamescom ONL 2022
snippet.description:
Glen Schofield, executive producer of Dead Space and the highly anticipated The Callisto Protocol, took the stage at Gamescom ONL 2022 to reveal an all new gameplay reveal for The Callisto Protocol. The gameplay trailer shows off abilities, weapons, as well as the enemy types you'll be encountering on your gruesome and terrifying journey.

#gaming #onl #gamescom #callistoprotocol
